<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="harm-vt">harm <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /hɑːrm/    美 /hɑːrm/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>伤害；损害：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Don't harm your eyes by reading in a poor light.
不要在微弱的灯光下看书，以免伤害眼睛。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Too much TV-watching can harm children's ability to learn.
看电视过多会影响孩子的学习能力。</p><footer>2010 辽宁</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>harmless /'hɑːmləs/ adj   </p></div>